data.description: This stunning brick home boasts 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and an impressive 3461 sq ft of living space. Situated on 1.56 acres, this home offers the perfect blend of country living and modern luxury. The open concept kitchen, complete with a double oven and breakfast bar, is perfect for preparing meals and entertaining guests. The huge bonus room over the garage is the ideal spot for a 5th bedroom, home theater or game room This home also offers plenty of space for relaxation. The oversized spa-like bathroom, with its jetted tub, provides a serene escape after a long day. With a welcoming porch, spacious deck, cozy fireplace, and balcony off the primary bedroom, you'll have no shortage of areas to unwind and relish the peaceful surroundings. Practical features include an attached two-car garage plus a detached two-car garage with a wood stove. There is also a large shed with power.  Appreciate this easy commute, just minutes from highways, shopping and restaurants.
